{"tid":1907383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得返工反而無返學咁大壓力？","createTime":"2020-03-02T14:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T05:49:40.000Z","uid":226310,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a6361e8c9250cdde7f6f6bcfb3be529a5fde8dc0","tid":1907383,"uid":226310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"啲大過你嘅人成日似住你未做過佢個位，講到自己個位幾撚難做，然後係咁講好掛住做你個位，講到你做啲野幾撚易幾撚輕鬆，講到自己好似好撚勁好撚捱得咁，但其實到你慢慢長大發覺其實2樣野根本唔同無得比，甚之自由度比以前高左同啲野對慣左，反而比以前輕鬆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00fd9b2810beb59cd9fb1ded32e0a62f54c034a","tid":1907383,"uid":126001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"cfd37c2de48890d851e2e6dab12b52a7aa8f7840","tid":1907383,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUkY6gk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUkY6gk.gif&h=54d7bf00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e46671e4ee3801b72d395e9a5f6c9d0aa9e6177","tid":1907383,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"唔係，返工壓力大好多<br />\nChing返邊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dee8647f5519773c9e497aa695cda698366da6","tid":1907383,"uid":226310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfd37c2de48890d851e2e6dab12b52a7aa8f7840","tid":1907383,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUkY6gk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUkY6gk.gif&h=54d7bf00&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"Jm9"},{"pid":"d8f3e7fd51c572b055c5bbd39665c044caa3f547","tid":1907383,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪仲後生<br />\n我後生時剛